-- Coltejer Investors Approve Reverse Split for Colombian Shares
-- B y   A n d r e a   J a r a m i l l o
-- 2012-04-10T13:14:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-10/coltejer-investors-approve-reverse-split-for-colombian-shares.html
Coltejer SA (COLTEJ) , a Colombian clothing
maker and exporter, said its shareholders approved a reverse
share split of 10,000 shares for one.  The split will be carried out starting May 2, the company
said in a regulatory filing yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Jaramillo in Bogota at 
